    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Finely slice 1/2 your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> into rounds and set them aside for garnish</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chilli</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Trim the <strong>green stalk</strong> off your <strong>aubergine[s]</strong> and chop into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
