    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> and<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[525ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the juice of 1/2 your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, your<strong> lime leaves </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and mix to combine – this is your <strong>aromatic stock</strong></p>",
