    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>aromatic stock</strong> to the pan with the <strong>Tenderstem</strong> <strong>broccoli stems </strong>and<strong> halved sugar snap peas</strong>, then reduce the heat to medium and cook for 3 min</p><p>Add the <strong>Tenderstem broccoli tips</strong> and cook for 2 min further or until everything's tender with a slight bite and the sauce has thickened slightly – this is your <strong>Thai green vegetable curry</strong></p>",
