    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Thai green vegetable curry</strong> with the <strong>basmati rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), the <strong>roasted peanuts</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
